---
title: Sticky Ginger Beef & Veggie Stir-Fry with Nutty Garlic Rice
description: A zap of ginger, a splash of oyster sauce and for the final ingredient in our flavour potion, a good dollop of sweet chilli sauce. Dip the beef mince into it and watch as a delicious dinner comes to life before your eyes. This beef mince and veggie stir-fry will be irresistible to anyone who takes a bite. Simply magical!
